ovn: ovn (Open Virtual Network - a software network switch)
ovn:
ovn: OVN (Open Virtual Network) is a series of daemons that translates
ovn: virtual network configuration into OpenFlow, and installs them into
ovn: Open vSwitch. It is licensed under the open source Apache 2 license.
ovn:
ovn: OVN provides a higher-layer abstraction than Open vSwitch, working
ovn: with logical routers and logical switches, rather than flows. OVN is
ovn: intended to be used by cloud management software (CMS).
ovn:
